text.div: • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActStatus where concept is-a normal

name: ActStatusNormal
title: ActStatusNormal
description: Encompasses the expected states of an Act, but excludes "nullified" and "obsolete" which represent unusual terminal states for the life-cycle.
